Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Removes the specified amount of ammo from the player's inventory.

Usage
-----

*void* useAmmo( *value'* )

Parameters
----------

-   [value] - The amount of ammo to consume.

Examples
--------

    Â 
    useAmmo( 1 );

Notes
-----

This script event does not return any values.

